bioRxiv subjects

Source: R/data.R
subjects.Rd

Names of subjects with RSS feeds in biorXiv

Usage

subjects

Format

A list of character vectors of subjects, one for bioRxiv, one for medRxiv.

References

https://www.biorxiv.org/alertsrss

Examples

subjects
